title: The 20 Million Journey | Dedicated To All My Fans | Ashish Chanchlani & Team
description:
Kaise ho sab log?
Ye dekho maine hafte pehle ye video edit ki
Jab main iss video ko edit kar raha tha i got way too emotional
I had tears when this finished.
I cannot believe this hum sabko saath mein 6 saal ho gaye?
From being an engineering student to a â€œcelebrityâ€? Celebrity shayad bann toh gaye lekin dil mein ab bhi wohi college student waali feeling aati hai
This is something i never imagined
Aur 2 CRORE SUBSCRIBERS? Mazak chal raha hai kyağŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ muje toh bas 100k karne the
Kaha pahucha diya bhai?
Who would have thought?
Ye video, ye journey, ye puri life main aap sab fans ko dedicate karta hu
I think one of the major reasons you all connect to me and show so much of love is because you see yourself in me
Which is absolutely true
I am one of you, my videos are based on you all, and nothing in my life gives me more happiness than seeing you all laugh and enjoy our work
Main aur meri puri team ACV ki taraf se ye video ek bahut bada thank you hai aap logo ko
3 mahine ke lambe dark depressing time ke baad ab jaake dil dimaag mein jaan aayi hai all THANKS TO YOU.
Aap ye 100 baar sun chuke ho ki how much you all mean to us but iâ€™ll still say this again
YOU ALL MEAN THE MOST TO US
WE LOVE YOU.
Thank you for giving this ordinary boy and extraordinary career to live.
Comment a special memory you have with me or my videosâ¤ï¸ğŸ™ğŸ¥º
I wanna thank some major people in my life journey : My parents, Muskan, Karishma Bhatia, Kunal chhabhria, Akash Dodeja, Simran Dhanwani, Jashan Sirwani, Tanish Sirwani, Anmol Sachar, Rohit Sadhwani, Ritesh Sadhwani, Grishim Nawani, Aditya Chanchlani, Suhan Chanchlani,Minesh Santani, Jacky Chawla, Karan gidwani, Prithvi Nathani, Sid Kedare, Deepak Sampat, Akshata sonawane, Akash Jagtap, Yogesh Makhija, Raaj Raisinghani & Navjyot Chandnani.
Sorry if i missed someone

title: Lockdown Ke Side Effects | Ashish Chanchlani
description:
#AshishChanchlani #LockdownKeSideEffects #ACVIANS
Dekho chota sa hi description bata ta hu, 
Ek hi tripod aur mobile se pura video shoot kiya hai toh professional nai lagega lekin kaam chala lo, make up muskan se karwaya, matlab mu pe mooch maskara se lagayi usse make up ka bada naam deke aap logo ko maja de raha hu 
aur batau? ye video ka naam 2020 expectations vs reality tha  lekin expectation ki shooting kar nai sakte the kyunki social distancing zaroori hai bhai, bahar jaake bevkoofo ki tarah shooting thodi karenge aur toh aur harsh beniwal bhi aisa kuch similiar bana raha tha (phone pe baat karte hum, whatsapp number hai mere paas uska) toh socha title change kardu warna log copy copy bolenge hum dono ko tanng karenge 

Wo online class waala script pechle video ke baad likha tha fir bb ne angry masterji 15 daal diya toh pure jokes change kiye warna firse log hum dono ko copy copy bolke tanng karte the (uska bhi whatsapp number tha, lekin bb bada seth aadmi hai hum gareebo ko yaad nai karta)

Finally 15 din, 8 sar dard ki goliya aur 300 kilo bhojan ke baad ye video ki kaise to script likhi muj jaise sust aadmi ne din raat ek karke ye video khud hi shoot ki edit ki (haan thumbnail kunal chhabhria ne banaya hai)
